{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"typedef","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"void (^)(NSString *, NSError *)","preciseIdentifier":"c:BFv(#*$objc(cs)NSString#*$objc(cs)NSError)","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This closure is called when the device registration process finishes, either successfully or with an error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The handler receives two parameters:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"token","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": The push token string if registration succeeded, or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if it failed"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"error"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": An error object if registration failed, or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" if it succeeded","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle registration result with UI updates and backend sync:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["func registerForNotifications() {","    let registrationHandler: PushwooshRegistrationHandler = { token, error in","        if let error = error {","            self.logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","            self.updateNotificationStatus(.failed)","            return","        }","","        guard let token = token else { return }","","        self.logger.info(\"Push token received: \\(token.prefix(20))...\")","        self.updateNotificationStatus(.registered)","","        self.syncPushTokenWithBackend(token)","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(withCompletion: registrationHandler)","}","","func syncPushTokenWithBackend(_ token: String) {","    let hwid = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","    apiClient.post(\"\/devices\/register\", body: [","        \"push_token\": token,","        \"hwid\": hwid,","        \"platform\": \"ios\"","    ])","}"],"type":"codeListing"}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Completion handler called when push notification registration completes."}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshFramework"}],"title":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","symbolKind":"typealias","externalID":"c:PWTypes.h@T@PushwooshRegistrationHandler","roleHeading":"Type Alias","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshRegistrationHandler"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshregistrationhandler"]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Related Documentation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshErrorHandler"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Push notification SDK for iOS applications.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework",